Name: Joe Smith
EventApi__Bio__c:
Come hear Joe speak about his experiences.

Joe was one of the first 50 consultants certified by Salesforce.com to provide services to their clients. Joe holds a Bachelor degree in Accounting, a Masters Degree in Taxation and is a Certified Public Accountant. He started his career as a senior manager with Ernst and Young. Joe has served as an investor, advisor and co-founder of multiple fast-growing technology companies.
